nodes.text: Will Sliney (born November 19, 1982) is a comics artist from Cork, Ireland. After getting his start in the UK and Ireland small press, he has drawn Farscape: Strange Detractors and the ongoing Farscape series from Boom! Studios. He is a member of the Eclectic Micks, an Irish collective sketchblog. He drew the two-parter "Dug Out"/"Outgunned" for the UK Star Wars: The Clone Wars comic in 2011.
He worked as an artist on the 40-page one-shot comic Beckett 1, which serves as a tie-in for the Solo: A Star Wars Story film, and penciled the comic adaptation for Solo: A Star Wars Story.
